{"title":"TARV Triumeq-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/TARV Triumeq-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Triumeq","guid":"jT8zQsghLdH4lutE08lnNQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Composición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Abacavir (ABC) 600 mg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Dolutegravir (DTG) 50 mg","guid":"lNh8wYkwfGgR-_O5ludmcw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Lamivudine (3TC) 300 mg","guid":"fj774UlWQkRDh6xuxWfYlQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• VIH.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Pacientes HLA-B*5701 negativos.","guid":"EcWxlo52wYO6VMjZjVm1Qg","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Presentación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Comprimidos para adultos.","guid":"5rVBEhwT1YVfBO-npwZPQA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Comprimidos dispersables (PD) para niños (10-<25 kg).","guid":"TnTPPcOkA1azKKTO1ZKMVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Dosificación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Adultos: 1 comprimido/día. (con/sin alimentos)","guid":"SeOqZxpd-GWWBN1WZCUHHg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Pediátrica:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"• 10-<14 kg: 4 PD/día","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"• 14-<20 kg: 5 PD/día","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"• 20-<25 kg: 6 PD/día","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"11","text":"• ≥25 kg: 1 comprimido adulto/día","guid":"1aEWSrvgSvK4wWHT4otu1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Renal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl ≥30: 1 comprimido/día.","guid":"pD0gGl-soFEK-XBNbgwAmw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• CrCl <30: No usar.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Ajuste Hepático:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• Contraindicado en insuficiencia moderada-severa (Child-Pugh B o C).","guid":"ZhNYc7BJlP4GwjE-VJigqw","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Efectos Adversos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Reacciones de hipersensibilidad (ABC, DTG).","guid":"VBfHMbf2VuoeEF0CK4aXbg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Exacerbación de hepatitis B (al suspender 3TC en coinfectados).","guid":"faIf99R1B3z8nQN15eI9_g","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"• Hepatotoxicidad, acidosis láctica, IRIS.","guid":"TtJGGy2EXkmKlJVpgH42rA","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"0","text":"Categoría en Embarazo:","guid":"t_A1o5u_YXUxgCH-7zv2sw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Combinación preferida (HHS, 2019).","guid":"p7srixFmnqa-ZHiA5FmRWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Lactancia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Opción razonable con CV suprimida durante el embarazo.","guid":"GQ__ODHVewRcHhOKn1MBig","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones\\NMedicamentosas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• ↓DTG: Antiácidos, suplementos Ca/Fe, carbamazepina, efavirenz, fosamprenavir/ritonavir, rifampina.","guid":"4bl0DCHayLsRoBdXZA9KeA","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• → Dosis DTG adicional.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"• Contraindicado: Dofetilide, nevirapina, fenobarbital, fenitoína.","guid":"iz0wf0yxUDV5pKDe54A39w","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"• Monitorizar/ajustar: Dalfampridina, metformina, metadona, riociguat.","guid":"GREoj4SIYl6VNsX3deZung","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"• Evitar: Sucralfato, hierba de San Juan, oxcarbazepina, sorbitol, etravirina.","guid":"ekXFt3iGTdpIRCv80TTiVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Clase: INSTI + 2 NRTI.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Absorción oral: ABC 83%, 3TC 86%.","guid":"O-QDFfbf1Cj_WLlelz7svg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Tmax: ABC 1.3 h, DTG 2-3 h.","guid":"blbleAER_wXrFm4ZFDC35A","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"• Unión proteínas: ABC 50%, DTG ≈99%, 3TC <36%.","guid":"wPsXB93opYdakp4A6ebhKw","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"• Vd: ABC 0.86 L/kg, DTG 17.4 L, 3TC 1.3 L/kg.","guid":"sjAJ5S5HTZOtv4176SCfqQ","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"• T1/2: ABC 1.5 h, DTG 14 h, 3TC 5-7 h.","guid":"hDlBvQVXNsj7gQCG5JJeGA","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"37","text":"• Eliminación: ABC (metabólico, no CYP), DTG (metabólico), 3TC (renal).","guid":"p2k1KiJABoebQJzfkybspA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"1. Triumeq Prescribing\\NInformation. Updated Apr 29,\\N2024.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":46,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"TARV Triumeq-2024-1","id":"map_1182","resolved_references":[]}